# StateWeave Terminal Demo
# Run with: vhs demo.tape
# Install VHS: brew install charmbracelet/tap/vhs

Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set Padding 20

Type "pip install stateweave"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "python examples/quickstart.py"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "stateweave doctor"
Enter
Sleep 3s
